    {
      "name": "Socket Events",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Socket.io Connection Guide",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{ws_url}}"
            }
          },
          "description": "Use a Socket.IO client to connect with auth token. Example JavaScript:\n\n```javascript\nconst socket = io('{{ws_url}}', {\n  auth: { token: '{{access_token}}' }\n});\n```"
        },
        {
          "name": "Rider: ride:search",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{ws_url}}" }
          },
          "description": "Emit event from rider socket:\n\n```javascript\nsocket.emit('ride:search', {\n  pickup: { lat: 23.8103, lng: 90.4125, address: 'Dhaka' },\n  drop: { lat: 23.7806, lng: 90.4000, address: 'Gulshan' },\n  vehicleType: 'auto',\n  couponCode: 'DISCOUNT10'\n}, callback);\n```"
        },
        {
          "name": "Rider: ride:book",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{ws_url}}" }
          },
          "description": "Emit event from rider socket:\n\n```javascript\nsocket.emit('ride:book', {\n  pickup: { lat: 23.8103, lng: 90.4125, address: 'Dhaka' },\n  drop: { lat: 23.7806, lng: 90.4000, address: 'Gulshan' },\n  vehicleType: 'auto',\n  couponCode: 'DISCOUNT10',\n  paymentMethod: 'cash'\n}, callback);\n```"
        },
        {
          "name": "Rider: ride:cancel",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{ws_url}}" }
          },
          "description": "Emit event from rider socket:\n\n```javascript\nsocket.emit('ride:cancel', { rideId: '<rideId>', reason: 'Changed plan' }, callback);\n```"
        },
        {
          "name": "Rider: rider:cancel_search",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{ws_url}}" }
          },
          "description": "Emit event from rider socket:\n\n```javascript\nsocket.emit('rider:cancel_search', { rideId: '<rideId>' });\n```"
        },
        {
          "name": "Rider: rider:ping",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{ws_url}}" }
          },
          "description": "Emit event from rider socket:\n\n```javascript\nsocket.emit('rider:ping');\nsocket.on('rider:pong', data => console.log(data));\n```"
        },
